PN,39201
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1780851961
OL,3,CVillage hit by 'big thud' earthquake
OL,4,Cfor second time in three weeks
OL,6,FA village has been hit by an
OL,7,Fearthquake for the second time in
OL,8,Fthree weeks - with residents
OL,9,Fdescribing it as "a burst of noise"
OL,10,Fand "a big thud".
OL,12,FLocals in Silverdale, a picturesque
OL,13,Fvillage in Lancashire, near the border
OL,14,Fwith Cumbria, reported the quake,
OL,15,Fsounding "like a distant explosion" on
OL,16,F6 June.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1780851961
OL,3,CVillage hit by 'big thud' earthquake
OL,4,Cfor second time in three weeks
OL,6,FAlongside Silverdale, it was felt in
OL,7,FCarnforth, Arnside, Milnthorpe, Burton-
OL,8,Fin-Kendal, Grange-over-Sands and
OL,9,Fsurrounding villages, with some
OL,10,Fresidents reporting a noise "like a
OL,11,Fneighbour had slammed a heavy door".
OL,13,FThe British Geological Survey (BGS)
OL,14,Freported a 2.2 magnitude earthquake
OL,15,Fhit at around 9.35pm at a depth of 3km
OL,16,Fin the Morecambe bay area.
OL,18,FThe same area was hit by a 2.3
OL,19,Fmagnitude earthquake on 13 May, and
OL,20,Falso a much smaller 0.4 magnitude
OL,21,Fearthquake on 12 April.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1780851961
OL,3,CVillage hit by 'big thud' earthquake
OL,4,Cfor second time in three weeks
OL,6,FA number of other earthquakes have
OL,7,Falso occurred in the area since the
OL,8,Fend of 2025, including in February and
OL,9,FMarch, as well as two in December 2025.
OL,11,FIn a post on Facebook, BGS said: "BGS:
OL,12,FBGS Seismic information... Silverdale,
OL,13,FLancashire 06 JUNE 2026 21:35 UTC 2.2
OL,14,FML The following preliminary
OL,15,Finformation is available for this
OL,16,Fearthquake.
OL,18,F"DATE: 06 June 2026 ORIGIN TIME: 21:35
OL,19,F32s UTC LAT/LON: 54.168 North /
OL,20,F2.832 West GRID REF: 346 kmE / 475
OL,21,FkmN DEPTH: 3 km MAGNITUDE: 2.2 Ml
OL,26,@{D@XOX|D@FOX
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
