PN,39206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1780851961
OL,3,CVillage hit by 'big thud' earthquake
OL,4,Cfor second time in three weeks
OL,6,FA magnitude 4 earthquake happens in
OL,7,FBritain roughly every two years. We
OL,8,Fexperience a magnitude 5 roughly every
OL,9,F10`20 years.
OL,11,FResearch suggests that the largest
OL,12,Fpossible earthquake in the UK is
OL,13,Faround magnitude 6.5.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
